                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col mb-4">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="~/css/doc2.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title">Dr J Vijayan</h4>
                <h5 class="card-text">General Physician</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    A well-known Physician with over 18 years of experience.
                    Using his immense knowledge and experience, he treats general conditions like diabetes,
                    anxiety, respiratory diseases, infectious diseases, digestive problems, urinary problems,
                    and abdominal.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col mb-4">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="~/css/doc3.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title">Dr Ahmed Ali</h4>
                <h5 class="card-text">Orthopaedics</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    He has specialized in arthroplasty of the hip and
                    knee and is also an expert in major orthopedic trauma including life
                    threatening pelvic injuries. He has
                    completed several clinical fellowships in pelviacetabular surgery, hip and
                    knee replacement surgery at prestigious institutions under experts at the
                    Singapore General Hospital
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
